## 8. Enforcement

When modifying any file listed in this document:
1. Check this document for known issues affecting that file.
2. Fix all P1 issues in the same changeset — no exceptions.
3. Fix P2 issues in the same changeset when the fix is under 30 minutes effort.
4. Log P3 issues as TODOs if not fixing immediately, but prefer fixing them.
5. Never introduce new instances of any anti-pattern listed above.
6. When creating new pages or components, verify they do not replicate any pattern from the "Consistency Violations" table.
